complement = fuz.fuzzy_not(tri_a1)
alg_prod = tri_a1 * tri_b1

intersection = fuz.fuzzy_and(x,a_pie,x,b_pie)
complement = fuz.fuzzy_not(a_pie)
alg_prod = a_pie * b_pie

Generalised bell¶

In [70]:
a=55
b=10
c=25

a1=65
b1=15
c1=45

a_pie = fuz.membership.gbellmf(x, a, b, c)

b_pie = fuz.membership.gbellmf(x, a1, b1, c1)

union= fuz.fuzzy_or(x,a_pie,x,b_pie)
intersection = fuz.fuzzy_and(x,a_pie,x,b_pie)
complement = fuz.fuzzy_not(a_pie)
alg_prod = a_pie * b_pie
